    {
        "content": "<p>Not exactly what you are looking for but I would point you to section 11.7 of Jacobs' <em>Categorical Logic and Type Theory</em> where he discusses relationships between interesting logical properties and the fibration being a stack. He is interested in the codomain fibration because it interprets dependent type theory rather than the subobject fibration.</p>",
